      <p>A credit card provides a line of credit that you can use for purchases and repay over time. It offers a convenient way to manage your spending, with benefits like rewards, cash back, and the ability to build your credit score. Unlike personal loans, credit cards offer ongoing access to funds and flexible repayment options.</p>
