          <li><strong>Low Interest Rates:</strong> Enjoy competitive interest rates that help you save on finance charges and make it easier to manage your balance.</li>
          <li><strong>Flexible Repayment Options:</strong> Choose from various repayment plans that suit your financial situation, including minimum payments or full balance pay-off options.</li>
