      <ul>
          <li><strong>Rewards Credit Cards:</strong> Earn points for every purchase, which can be redeemed for travel, merchandise, or gift cards. Perfect for those who want to earn while they spend.</li>
          <li><strong>Cash Back Credit Cards:</strong> Get a percentage of your spending back as cash rewards. Ideal for everyday purchases and saving on your monthly expenses.</li>
          <li><strong>Travel Credit Cards:</strong> Enjoy travel-related perks such as free checked bags, priority boarding, and travel insurance. Designed for frequent travelers looking for added benefits.</li>
          <li><strong>Balance Transfer Credit Cards:</strong> Transfer high-interest balances from other cards to enjoy lower interest rates and reduce your debt faster. Great for consolidating debt and saving on interest.</li>
          <li><strong>Student Credit Cards:</strong> Tailored for students to help build credit history and manage expenses while offering features designed for new credit users.</li>
      </ul>
  </section>

